    public class JukeboxView
extends javafx.scene.layout.BorderPane
    Author:
    Ashley Mains and Victor Gomes CLASS: JukeboxView DESCRIPTION: Builds the GUI JukeboxView and provides all interaction implementation for buttons and text boxes. The view can be set to show different options based on the user (admin vs. user).
